{"tid":1282741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葡領館接獲港人查詢明顯增加","createTime":"2019-07-03T15:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:53:20.000Z","uid":10970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb04bd3dc4098971ea101c275f753ed047566ce","tid":1282741,"uid":10970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"葡領館接獲港人查詢明顯增加<br />\n<br />\n14 分鐘前   香港  有所準備<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月3日｜譯自 葡文澳門電台<br />\n<br />\n葡文澳門電台報導，香港居民對葡萄牙駐港澳總領事館的需求有所增加。<br />\n<br />\n葡領館向澳廣視葡文新聞表示，過去五個星期以來，接獲香港人對有關申請國籍、居留簽證以及更新過期文件的查詢有所增加。<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙駐港澳總領事歐冠溢表示，手上沒有統計數據，但證實最近有很多港人查詢，以及續期葡萄牙護照，當中有些是已在數年前過期。<br />\n<br />\n歐冠溢表示，在過去五星期，這類的查詢有明顯上升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mediajose.tumblr.com/post/186026471653/%E8%91%A1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmediajose.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F186026471653%2F%25E8%2591%25A1%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=925c8426\" target=\"_blank\">https://mediajose.tumblr.com/post/186026471653/%E8%91%A1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0</a>"},{"pid":"03ae63c2b436176e7679e730bcf858982e82215b","tid":1282741,"uid":10970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}